      <trans-unit id="about.heading" datatype="html">
        <source>Engineering systems that <x id="START_TAG_SPAN" ctype="x-span" equiv-text="&lt;span id=&quot;header-content_highlight&quot;&gt;"/> scale beyond <x id="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" ctype="x-span" equiv-text="&lt;/span&gt;"/> the interface. </source>
        <target>Des systèmes conçus pour <x id="START_TAG_SPAN" ctype="x-span" equiv-text="&lt;span id=&quot;header-content_highlight&quot;&gt;"/> dépasser <x id="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" ctype="x-span" equiv-text="&lt;/span&gt;"/> l'interface. </target>
